Rudzani Matshili Chief of the South African National Defence Force (SANDF), General Solly Shoke this morning conferred medals to members of the SANDF for their service and professionalism.  The proceedings took place by means of a parade at the Armscor sportsground in Erasmuskloof, Pretoria.  
Shoke said the medals were for the member's loyalty and hard work.  
