He also thanked the recipient's families for their support. "I would like to thank the families of the recipients here on parade for the support that you have been giving them because without your support I don't think they would have been strong enough to be able to achieve what they have achieved today,"he said.   
"Lastly I would like to thank the recipients on parade, you are shining example and a mirror." 
Medals also symbolise loyalty and dedication to the course of defending the territorial integrity of the Republic and are conferred as a token of appreciation to members.